00:32.597 --> 00:33.637
Get up!

00:35.557 --> 00:37.156
What time is it?

00:37.157 --> 00:40.397
Time you did some work.
Lying around like a useless lump!

00:41.637 --> 00:44.396
Sorry, Dad. I don't feel well.

00:44.397 --> 00:46.997
You think I take the day off
when I feel poorly?

00:48.157 --> 00:49.317
Feeble little runt!

00:53.637 --> 00:55.797
Look at you. Pathetic!

00:57.917 --> 00:59.756
You're meant to be a man!

00:59.757 --> 01:03.637
But what did I expect?
You take after your mother.

01:05.837 --> 01:07.276
What did you say?

01:07.277 --> 01:08.916
You heard.

01:08.917 --> 01:10.997
You're just like your mother.

01:18.957 --> 01:21.916
I'm nothing like my mother!

01:21.917 --> 01:25.117
Pathetic, am I? A little runt?
Get off me!

01:26.517 --> 01:28.717
Why should I?
Now who's the feeble one?

01:34.117 --> 01:36.516
Things are going to change around
here, Dad.

01:36.517 --> 01:38.117
Things are going to change!

